    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## 1. 資料讀取與原始變數檢查\n",
        "## (Data Loading and Initial Variable Inspection)\n",
        "\n",
        "**中文說明：**\n",
        "在此步驟中，我們將讀取小組已清理且重編碼完成的資料集 `cleaned_data.csv`。我們將驗證有效樣本的總列數，並初步檢視核心比較群體（感到悲傷或絕望：`SadOrHopeless_Recoded`）與反應變數（目前吸菸狀況：`CurrentCigaretteUse_Recoded`）之間的原始交叉計數。\n",
        "\n",
        "**English Description:**\n",
        "In this step, we load the pre-processed and recoded dataset `cleaned_data.csv`. We will verify the total effective sample size and perform an initial inspection of the cross-tabulation between our core grouping variable (Sadness Status: `SadOrHopeless_Recoded`) and the response variable (Smoking Status: `CurrentCigaretteUse_Recoded`)."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "8eJu2C2t14Bl"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "\n",
        "# 1. 讀取資料\n",
        "df = pd.read_csv('/content/cleaned_data.csv')\n",
        "print(\"資料讀取成功！總筆數：\", len(df))\n",
        "\n",
        "# 設定你們資料集標準的欄位名稱\n",
        "sad_col = 'SadOrHopeless_Recoded'\n",
        "smoke_col = 'CurrentCigaretteUse_Recoded'\n",
        "\n",
        "# 檢查這兩個欄位的交叉計數，確保資料沒問題\n",
        "print(\"\\n--- 兩欄位原始交叉次數分配 ---\")\n",
        "print(pd.crosstab(df[sad_col], df[smoke_col], margins=True))"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "Xa2dxQ4_2I6K",
        "outputId": "8876fe3b-d5d0-4523-9843-db4ad12dc3fe"
